{
  "version": "1.1.3",
  "releaseNotes": {
    "zh": [
      "新增 DOC、DOCX、PDF、TXT、RTF、ODT 等文档批量导入，按换行快速加入单词或短语。",
      "将未找到、模糊匹配与生成完成信息合并为一个窗口，并用可滚动列表保持界面紧凑。",
      "增强精确搜索的容错与备用词典来源，避免可用的常见单词因单个网络服务失败而被跳过。",
      "PDF 会突出显示模糊匹配后的正确单词，并以较小灰字保留用户原始输入。"
    ],
    "en": [
      "Added newline-based bulk import from DOC, DOCX, PDF, TXT, RTF, ODT, and other document formats.",
      "Combined missing terms, fuzzy matches, and completion actions into one compact dialog with a scrollable result list.",
      "Improved exact-search resilience and dictionary fallback so a single optional provider failure cannot hide common words.",
      "PDF exports now show the corrected fuzzy-match term prominently and retain the original input in smaller gray text."
    ]
  },
